## <a id="collected"></a>Data collected

The Collector collects data about how your product portfolio is
configured and maintained. It does not collect any personal data or
information related to an identified or identifiable natural person; for
example, it does not collect Ops Manager’s free text fields such as
passwords, private keys or other authentication-type tools. Note that we
collect configuration information for all products installed across the
portfolio, which may include the below information for partner tiles as
well.

The Collector connects to Ops Manager on any PCF foundation for which it
is provided valid credentials and collects the following data in a
compressed archive on the local filesystem:

